room_title: Escape room "Zodiac Killer: Legacy" by The Exit Game in San Antonio
room_address: 5720 Bandera Rd STE 23, San Antonio, TX 78238
room_description: The infamous Zodiac killer has returned. You have been trapped in his lair and must join your fellow prisoners and escape before he returns. But before you do, find the evidence you need to find his true identity and put an end to his killing spree forever! Do you have what it takes to find the clues and solve the mystery that has haunted Americans for the last 30 years?
